<p>The <b>song sparrow</b> (<i>Melospiza melodia</i>) is a medium-sized <a href="/wiki/American_sparrow" title="American sparrow">American sparrow</a>. Among the native sparrows in <a href="/wiki/North_America" title="North America">North America</a>, it is easily one of the most abundant, variable and adaptable species.</p>
<p></p>
